towards moon of full purpose,

26:05.361 --> 26:08.196
and see blood and gore matted upon fur.

26:09.264 --> 26:10.865
Curfew!
<i>Inside please.</i>

26:10.933 --> 26:13.301
<i>Make your way indoors!</i>

26:13.369 --> 26:15.637
<i>Curfew!</i>
Move, move.

26:15.704 --> 26:16.638
Move along!

26:16.706 --> 26:17.639
<i>Off the streets!</i>

26:17.707 --> 26:18.640
<i>You move along!</i>

26:18.707 --> 26:23.445
<i>Clear these streets!</i>

26:30.086 --> 26:31.854
<i>Messalina!</i>

26:33.023 --> 26:36.592
She has a habit of running wild.

26:36.660 --> 26:38.227
Here.

26:38.295 --> 26:40.296
You stay close to your mother.

26:42.265 --> 26:44.299
Gratitude.

26:44.367 --> 26:45.934
You inside.

26:56.413 --> 26:57.579
<i>You there.</i>

27:03.919 --> 27:06.154
I laid eyes upon you
in the square this morning,

27:06.221 --> 27:09.691
did I not?
As I upon you.

27:09.758 --> 27:11.359
Word has reached ear you spoke my name

27:11.427 --> 27:14.829
upon entering gate, claiming business.

27:14.897 --> 27:16.998
I fear you have been misled.

27:17.066 --> 27:19.168
You have nothing I find of worth.

27:22.906 --> 27:24.707
Then why are you within these walls?

27:24.774 --> 27:25.874
Remove hand.

27:25.942 --> 27:27.676
What is your purpose here?

27:27.744 --> 27:30.679
Put question to honored
husband, and have reply.

27:30.747 --> 27:32.047
He trades with the Aedile?

27:32.115 --> 27:36.118
He does.

27:38.154 --> 27:41.256
The mistake is mine, then.

27:41.324 --> 27:44.493
See yourself from the streets
before nightfall,

27:44.560 --> 27:47.095
to avoid further misunderstanding.

27:52.134 --> 27:54.202
<i>Come along!</i>

27:54.270 --> 27:55.603
Apologies.

27:55.671 --> 27:58.573
I assure you, not all
in the city stand as him.

27:58.640 --> 28:01.542
What he spoke of, removing
myself from the streets...?

28:01.609 --> 28:03.710
Is it not troublesome?

28:03.778 --> 28:05.980
I made attempt to dissuade my husband,

28:06.047 --> 28:07.615
but he thought it best
to have streets cleared

28:07.682 --> 28:09.083
of all but city guard,

28:09.151 --> 28:13.221
<i>until the rebellion has been quelled.</i>

28:13.289 --> 28:15.323
You have a place
to call your own this night?

28:15.391 --> 28:18.060
Yes.

28:18.127 --> 28:20.996
I have my eye towards such.

28:35.211 --> 28:38.780
<i>Move inside!</i>

28:38.848 --> 28:40.409
<i>All streets are to be cleared!</i>

28:43.152 --> 28:44.720
<i>Curfew is in affect!</i>

28:44.787 --> 28:46.788
<i>A little more securer this time!</i>

28:59.469 --> 29:01.370
<i>The streets cleared by guards?</i>

29:01.438 --> 29:03.772
By command of the Aedile.

29:03.840 --> 29:04.940
Did you know of this?

29:05.008 --> 29:06.007
Fuck yourself.

29:06.075 --> 29:09.811
News greets me with shared ear.

29:09.879 --> 29:11.946
Trust these will service need.

29:17.919 --> 29:19.953
They will.

29:20.020 --> 29:21.888
Yet there is more
we must ask of you now.

29:23.290 --> 29:24.623
I thought as much.

29:24.691 --> 29:26.959
Two hundred denarii a piece,

29:27.027 --> 29:28.747
<i>and you may lay hidden</i>
<i>here until sun crests</i>

29:28.795 --> 29:31.263
and curfew is lifted.

29:31.331 --> 29:33.399
It is not sleep we seek.

29:33.466 --> 29:35.668
What deformity of mind
do you think I suffer from,

29:35.735 --> 29:38.170
that I would give further
aid to enemies of Rome?

29:38.238 --> 29:41.140
We find ourselves heavy with Roman coin.

29:41.208 --> 29:46.379
<i>What cost would sober intent?</i>

29:46.447 --> 29:50.250
Five thousand denarii would
see me far from this city,

29:50.318 --> 29:53.654
and shores of fucking Republic.

29:53.722 --> 29:54.855
A bargain well struck.

29:57.494 --> 29:59.561
Call me Roman no more, then!

29:59.629 --> 30:00.729
How many more swords do you need?

30:00.797 --> 30:04.232
<i>Those that join us are well armed.</i>

30:06.268 --> 30:08.369
Join you?

30:08.437 --> 30:11.440
You move to take the fucking city?!

30:11.507 --> 30:13.075
We move to liberate it.

30:13.142 --> 30:15.210
The gate stands only in our path.

30:15.278 --> 30:17.012
We would to slit throats in the night

30:17.079 --> 30:18.246
and see it raised.

30:18.314 --> 30:20.582
<i>Unexpected curfew presents difficulty</i>

30:20.650 --> 30:22.384
in reaching it unnoticed.

30:22.452 --> 30:25.454
City guard would raise
clamor well in advance --

30:34.398 --> 30:37.233
I cannot aid you in this.

30:37.301 --> 30:41.971
It would mean my life.

30:42.039 --> 30:46.910
You have forged weapons
for Spartacus himself.

30:46.978 --> 30:51.047
If we are discovered with
your craft clutched in hand,

30:51.115 --> 30:54.284
then they will send you
to the afterlife all the same.

30:57.990 --> 31:01.460
Fuck the gods.

31:01.527 --> 31:03.162
What would you have of me?

31:10.671 --> 31:12.138
Gently.

31:12.205 --> 31:15.808
I should not have content
fall to ruin by rough use.

31:15.876 --> 31:17.643
Go fetch the rest.

31:17.711 --> 31:19.211
See that they are careful.

31:25.285 --> 31:27.753
You would see me weighted
with unnecessary comforts.

31:28.821 --> 31:31.690
Have I grown that heavy?

31:31.757 --> 31:32.724
These are yours?

31:32.792 --> 31:34.493
I would not be found wanting,

31:34.560 --> 31:37.730
if campaign stretches
beyond expectation.

31:37.797 --> 31:40.466
You wish to join me,
in pursuit of Spartacus?

31:40.533 --> 31:42.535
I wish no such thing.

31:42.602 --> 31:44.437
Yet I will not be removed from your arms

31:44.505 --> 31:46.372
for months threatening years.

31:47.708 --> 31:50.143
Publius and I shall travel
with you and Tiberius.

31:50.211 --> 31:53.146
You know women are forbidden
within encampment.

31:53.214 --> 31:55.548
Yet they are not banned
from followers' camp,

31:55.616 --> 31:57.651
unless rules have shifted
absent knowledge.

31:59.020 --> 32:02.089
I would not have my family
bedded among slaves and whores.

32:02.157 --> 32:03.857
Is it not better solution

32:03.925 --> 32:07.494
than having them stricken from embrace?

32:10.064 --> 32:13.199
Desire much appreciated.

32:13.266 --> 32:16.236
Yet I could not stay mind
from thought of your safety,

32:16.303 --> 32:18.104
placed so near the enemy.

32:19.806 --> 32:22.308
I would have you remain here,

32:22.375 --> 32:26.678
far from the threat of death
war so often promises.

32:28.948 --> 32:32.685
Is that sole reason?

32:36.123 --> 32:38.090
Father.

32:38.158 --> 32:39.559
All has been attended.

32:39.626 --> 32:42.228
Your army stands ready
to march upon first light.

32:42.296 --> 32:44.030
News well received.

32:44.097 --> 32:47.099
I would have word.

32:47.167 --> 32:50.336
There yet lingers issue
of what title I shall hold.

32:50.403 --> 32:52.337
I am possessed of leanings
towards the matter.

32:52.405 --> 32:55.574
Morning sun shall
see them fall to place.

32:55.642 --> 32:58.310
Have these returned
from where they sprang.

32:58.377 --> 33:01.045
I would have house in order
before we take leave from it.

33:05.317 --> 33:08.721
I thought honored position all but mine.

33:08.788 --> 33:11.624
Now I fear he favors another.

33:11.692 --> 33:14.327
Then you stand as your mother,

33:14.395 --> 33:18.365
bound by blood and inconsiderate worth.

33:35.917 --> 33:38.718
<i>It is a thing of rare beauty.</i>

33:38.786 --> 33:40.386
Is it not?

33:40.454 --> 33:42.656
Yes, Dominus.

33:42.723 --> 33:46.425
You will carry it when
you face Spartacus?

33:46.493 --> 33:49.328
I shall carry my father's sword.

33:49.396 --> 33:53.065
<i>It is not as well bred</i>
<i>or considered as this...</i>

33:53.133 --> 33:54.733
<i>yet it holds deeper meaning.</i>

33:54.801 --> 33:56.469
Caesar will carry it then?

33:56.537 --> 34:00.907
As your word and will?

34:00.975 --> 34:04.411
I should not have placed
you within his reach.

34:04.478 --> 34:06.012
He is a man of base needs.

34:06.080 --> 34:10.949
Then why honor him with title,
that above your son?

34:11.018 --> 34:14.319
Apologies, I overstep.

34:15.388 --> 34:17.856
You speak your heart.

34:17.924 --> 34:19.958
I know your concern for the boy.

34:20.025 --> 34:22.726
He no longer stands as such.

34:22.793 --> 34:25.964
But in the eyes of his father.

34:27.331 --> 34:31.436
Would my wife could
voice such simple wisdom.

34:31.503 --> 34:33.705
I saw the gathering of trunks.

34:33.772 --> 34:35.206
She goes with you?

34:35.274 --> 34:37.475
It was her intent.

34:37.543 --> 34:43.181
Yet I would find
no comfort in her presence.

34:44.016 --> 34:46.552
As I would in yours...

34:48.855 --> 34:51.223
Is such a thing possible?

34:51.290 --> 34:54.259
I will be forced to place
you within followers' camp.

34:54.327 --> 34:57.328
But yes, it is possible.

34:57.396 --> 34:59.797
If you so desire it.

34:59.865 --> 35:03.133
Yes, Dominus.

35:03.201 --> 35:05.236
I do not pose question as master,

35:05.303 --> 35:07.538
but as a man.

35:07.605 --> 35:12.343
And would have answer as one.

35:12.411 --> 35:14.812
Yes.

35:14.880 --> 35:20.985
It is something I desire, Marcus.

35:55.620 --> 35:57.354
Fuck my ass...

36:05.431 --> 36:06.364
Quickly!

36:06.432 --> 36:08.567
We must gather more men and swords!

36:08.634 --> 36:12.805
Spartacus is here!

36:18.378 --> 36:19.846
The moon nears its peak.

36:19.913 --> 36:24.517
Yet fucking gate stands firmly rooted.

36:24.585 --> 36:27.453
They will see it raised.

36:27.521 --> 36:29.855
<i>Or fall in attempt.</i>

36:29.923 --> 36:31.290
Ready the others.

36:31.358 --> 36:34.793
When gate trembles,
death follows upon heel.

36:49.341 --> 36:50.508
<i>Spartacus is within our walls!</i>

36:50.576 --> 36:51.509
<i>Move, come with me.</i>

36:51.577 --> 36:53.044
See gate protected!

36:53.112 --> 36:54.812
<i>You, open the storeroom!</i>

36:56.015 --> 36:57.415
<i>Quickly!</i>

37:03.089 --> 37:05.624
Reward will surely find hands for this.

37:05.692 --> 37:09.728
Of that I have no fucking doubt.

37:21.375 --> 37:24.243
Attius!
<i>Raise the alarm --</i>

37:25.645 --> 37:26.712
<i>Call for more men!</i>

37:29.749 --> 37:32.251
Hide yourself, I will find
you when it is over!

38:08.790 --> 38:10.191
See gate opened!

38:10.258 --> 38:13.361
<i>Clear the way!</i>

38:32.315 --> 38:33.249
Move!

38:44.294 --> 38:46.362
Arm yourselves!

38:46.430 --> 38:48.231
Forward towards the front gate!

40:14.785 --> 40:16.419
Diotimus.

40:16.487 --> 40:18.087
Where is Laurus?

40:19.723 --> 40:21.591
I am here, slave.

40:27.733 --> 40:29.894
You would turn against your
dominus and join rebellion?

40:30.903 --> 40:32.103
Fucking animals...

40:53.794 --> 40:55.361
Diotimus.

40:58.532 --> 41:00.200
The villa is taken.

41:00.267 --> 41:01.735
See yourselves free.

41:03.103 --> 41:06.172
Move.

41:06.239 --> 41:08.107
My dominus...

41:08.175 --> 41:11.444
<i>He is dead?</i>

41:11.512 --> 41:15.315
Then I shall follow
him to the afterlife...

41:15.382 --> 41:18.251
