41:47.547 --> 41:49.481
I will follow once I find him.

41:49.549 --> 41:51.116
May the gods protect you.

41:53.553 --> 41:54.486
The Aedile.

41:54.554 --> 41:55.988
Have you seen the Aedile?

41:58.858 --> 41:59.892
You.

41:59.960 --> 42:01.727
You aid Spartacus?

42:01.795 --> 42:03.296
