43:01.321 --> 43:06.191
<i>I did not wish to stain</i>
<i>it with such business.</i>

43:06.259 --> 43:09.729
Years abroad led you
to strange pleasures,

43:09.796 --> 43:14.333
worthy of the beast you appear.

43:14.401 --> 43:18.304
And your father...
he's not spoken to you of this?

43:18.372 --> 43:22.108
