with more pressing concerns.

43:22.176 --> 43:24.978
Well, I'm certain
he will share confidence.

43:25.046 --> 43:29.850
When he deems you deserving.

43:29.917 --> 43:31.017
You think I am not?

43:33.688 --> 43:35.490
Sleep well, young master.

43:35.557 --> 43:38.560
And dream of future glories.

43:38.627 --> 43:40.528
Under my command.

44:38.054 --> 44:38.987
