if we were beneath heel?

45:07.551 --> 45:09.218
<i>Still, cunt!</i>

45:10.553 --> 45:11.887
Spartacus!

45:11.955 --> 45:13.890
<i>The Aedile bars himself in the horreum,</i>

45:13.957 --> 45:17.226
spilling pitch and threatens
to put light to bear.

45:17.294 --> 45:18.628
Come.

45:18.696 --> 45:22.865
I will not lend aid
to you and your animals.

45:22.933 --> 45:24.433
If grain is put to fire,

45:24.501 --> 45:30.105
even I will not have voice
to calm my "animals."

45:30.173 --> 45:31.407
<i>You will do this,</i>

45:31.475 --> 45:36.278
or see your people that
yet live fall from this world.

45:40.818 --> 45:43.086
Please.
<i>Stay still!</i>

46:06.411 --> 46:09.413
You will not have my city's heart!

46:09.481 --> 46:11.315
Kill them!

46:11.383 --> 46:13.684
Kill them!
