46:16.455 --> 46:19.457
Make attempt on gate
and I will for all to torch,

46:19.524 --> 46:20.892
you fucking cunts!

46:22.862 --> 46:24.429
I can take him...

46:24.497 --> 46:26.564
Agron!

46:26.632 --> 46:27.832
Lower spear.

46:31.471 --> 46:34.773
Laeta...

46:34.841 --> 46:35.974
<i>Kill them all!</i>

46:36.042 --> 46:37.175
Go to him.

46:37.243 --> 46:39.377
And pray your words hold meaning.

46:39.445 --> 46:41.179
<i>Don't listen to his words!</i>

46:41.247 --> 46:43.315
<i>He's the reason we suffered!</i>

46:47.954 --> 46:50.889
I thought you dead.

46:50.957 --> 46:53.591
You would place our fate
in her fucking hands.

46:53.659 --> 46:57.195
I place it in what I believe in.

46:57.262 --> 47:00.765
I yet live, among a clutch of others.

47:00.833 --> 47:01.833
How many?

47:01.900 --> 47:03.501
Too few.

47:03.569 --> 47:06.571
And we will be fewer still,
if you do not stop this.

47:06.639 --> 47:08.372
You would give them
all we have worked for?

47:08.440 --> 47:12.143
<i>I would see no more death this night.</i>

47:12.211 --> 47:16.480
Open gate, let us see sun
crest upon another day.

47:16.548 --> 47:18.549
I will not bow to fucking slaves!

47:18.617 --> 47:23.354
Turn thought from them,
and towards your people.

47:23.422 --> 47:25.323
If you do this,

47:25.390 --> 47:29.060
<i>you will condemn them</i>
<i>all to the afterlife.</i>

47:29.127 --> 47:30.294
Your wife among them...

47:39.071 --> 47:40.505
Oh, no!

48:00.293 --> 48:02.995
He would have opened the gate!

48:03.063 --> 48:04.430
I know he would of.

48:04.498 --> 48:06.799
He would have opened the gate for me.

48:06.866 --> 48:09.368
I could not place faith in it.

48:17.944 --> 48:22.314
We have had our fill of blood
and vengeance this night.

48:22.381 --> 48:27.719
No Roman that yet draws breath
shall suffer further harm.

48:27.786 --> 48:29.787
The city is ours!

48:31.557 --> 48:35.160
<i>The city is free!</i>

48:35.227 --> 48:37.295
<i>Once again the Romans fall!</i>

48:38.931 --> 48:40.765
<i>Victory!</i>

48:44.803 --> 48:50.175
<i>To see one loved robbed</i>
<i>of life is a heavy thing.</i>

48:50.242 --> 48:53.845
