one holds closest to heart

49:19.272 --> 49:20.773
struck from this world.

49:24.577 --> 49:27.012
I would not have
my son fall to such a fate

49:27.080 --> 49:31.116
<i>because he was not ready for command.</i>

49:31.184 --> 49:33.485
Nor would I deny him opportunity,

49:33.553 --> 49:36.654
