a man in his father's eyes.

49:43.495 --> 49:46.830
You stand as my word and my will.

49:50.768 --> 49:52.402
You honor me, father.

49:52.470 --> 49:55.272
As I shall honor the name of Crassus.

49:55.340 --> 49:58.242
<i>Ride with Caesar</i>
<i>and men of your choosing.</i>

49:58.310 --> 50:01.812
Seek out Mummius and what
remains of Cossinius' legion.

50:01.880 --> 50:04.348
